CROW, Appellant, v. COFFIN, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Moses R. Crow against William E. Coffin.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

A. Perry, for appellant. C. Norwood, for respondent

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements. See 27 N. Y. Supp. 1108.
